donations.donation_comment: Never use the GoFundMe illegal site.     Go Truckers!   Fight for Freedom!
Thank God for the Truckers standing up for Freedom!
Thank you for standing up for freedom. You are in my prayers

A huge thank you to our neighbors up north for your courage to stand for FREEDOM!! I am praying the LORD surrounds you and your families and keeps you all safe and warm!
May the LORD answer you when you are in distress; may the name of the God of Jacob protect you. Psalm 20:1  
In the mighty name of Jesus!
We the people. Thank you for protesting against vaccine mandates and the forever lockdown. You are an inspiration and sending our love and prayers. Peace be with You. Blessings

This tyranny must end! Let us support our truckers and each other however we can! Thank you truckers, volunteers and all the supporters in your fight for our freedoms. 
God Bless!

Thank you to these amazing truckers that had the guts to stand up and show us the way! Now they are giving strength to other people around the world! So inspiring! The love and positivity and stories of the Canadian people coming together is truly amazing! I have never felt prouder to be a Canadian!🇨🇦🇨🇦🇨🇦
